Hugh Osmond’s Horizon in Talks to Buy Fairfield Energy, Sky Says

-- B y   B e n j a m i n   P u r v i s
-- 
2011-03-18T10:50:04Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-18/hugh-osmond-s-horizon-in-talks-to-buy-fairfield-energy-sky-says.html
Hugh Osmond’s Horizon is in talks
to buy Fairfield Energy, Sky News reported, without saying where
it got the information.  Horizon has been in talks with Fairfield’s management for
several weeks and the transaction could be worth between 500
million pounds and 700 million pounds, Sky said on its website.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Benjamin Purvis at 
 bpurvis@bloomberg.net  